    <item>
      <title>Giao Thức HTTP: Methods và Status Codes</title>
      <link>https://example.org/posts/http-protocol/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 00:00:00 +0700</pubDate>
      <guid>https://example.org/posts/http-protocol/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-http-methods&#34;&gt;1. HTTP Methods&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GET&lt;/strong&gt;: Lấy dữ liệu.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;POST&lt;/strong&gt;: Gửi dữ liệu mới.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PUT&lt;/strong&gt;: Cập nhật toàn bộ.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PATCH&lt;/strong&gt;: Cập nhật một phần.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DELETE&lt;/strong&gt;: Xoá dữ liệu.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-status-codes&#34;&gt;2. Status Codes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2xx (Success)&lt;/strong&gt;: 200 OK, 201 Created.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3xx (Redirection)&lt;/strong&gt;: 301 Moved Permanently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4xx (Client Error)&lt;/strong&gt;: 400 Bad Request, 404 Not Found.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5xx (Server Error)&lt;/strong&gt;: 500 Internal Server Error.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
